OL,3,CCompany fined after apprentice suffers
OL,4,Csevere burns from blow torch
OL,6,FA boat maintenance company in Jersey
OL,7,Fhas been fined #20,000 after an
OL,8,Fapprentice suffered severe burns from
OL,9,Fa blow torch.
OL,11,FMorris Marine & Motors Ltd were
OL,12,Fprosecuted by the Health and Safety
OL,13,FInspectorate for failing to ensure the
OL,14,Fhealth and safety of their employees.
OL,16,FThey pleaded guilty to the offence at
OL,17,FJersey's Royal Court and alongside the
OL,18,Ffine, they will also have to pay
OL,19,F#5,000 in costs.
