OL,3,CCompany fined after apprentice suffers
OL,4,Csevere burns from blow torch
OL,6,FThe incident happened in July 2023
OL,7,Fwhen an apprentice, who had been
OL,8,Femployed by the company for just under
OL,9,Ftwo months, used a blow torch near a
OL,10,Fflammable brake cleaner while working
OL,11,Fon a boat's hull in dry dock.
OL,13,FHe was severely burned and had to be
OL,14,Ftransferred to Southampton for
OL,15,Ftreatment.
OL,17,FThere were "several significant
OL,18,Ffailures in the management of health
OL,19,Fand safety at Morris Marine and Motors
OL,20,FLtd which contributed to the
OL,21,Fincident", an investigation concluded.
